---
// Hero Section — light theme
---

<section class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">

  <div
    class="absolute inset-0"
    style="
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 48px 48px;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% 50%, black 20%, transparent 100%);
      -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% 50%, black 20%, transparent 100%);
    "
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <div
    class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"
    style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(8,145,178,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">

    <div
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] mb-8"
      style="color: #6b7280; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both;"
    >
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full animate-pulse" style="background: #0891b2;"></span>
      UPTIME: ALL SYSTEMS NOMINAL
    </div>

    <h1
      class="font-black text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl tracking-tight leading-none mb-4"
      style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; color: #111827; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.1s both;"
    >
      SYSTEM
      <span style="color: #0891b2;">ONLINE.</span>
    </h1>

    <div
      class="mt-5 mb-10 text-base sm:text-lg tracking-wide"
      style="font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.2s both;"
    >
      <span style="color: #d1d5db;">~/artemis $&nbsp;</span>
      <span style="color: #6b7280;">探索、记录与代码</span>
      <span class="inline-block w-[2px] h-[1.1em] ml-0.5 align-middle animate-[blink_1.1s_step-end_infinite]" style="background: #0891b2;"></span>
    </div>

    <p
      class="max-w-lg mx-auto text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide mb-12"
      style="color: #9ca3af; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.3s both;"
    >
      这里是我的数字据点 —— 记录硬件与嵌入式的探索历程、零散的技术思考，以及一些不值得发朋友圈但值得被留存的碎片。
    </p>

    <div
      class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4"
      style="animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.4s both;"
    >
      <a
        href="/blog"
        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-2.5 text-sm tracking-widest text-white rounded-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
        style="font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; background: #0891b2; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(8,145,178,0.25);"
      >
        读博客
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M2 7h10M8 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="/about"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-2.5 text-sm tracking-widest rounded-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
        style="font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; color: #6b7280; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);"
      >
        关于作者
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 pointer-events-none"
    style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, #fafafa);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50%       { opacity: 0; }
  }
</style>
